    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyLoad: yes
biocViews: Sequencing, DNASeq, SomaticMutation, Visualization,
    Clustering, GenomicVariation, StatisticalMethod, BiologicalQuestion
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
